    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Bathycongrus bimaculatus sp. nov., A, B. Holotype, NMMB-P24393, 163 mm TL. C. Paratype, NMMB-P7012, 157 mm TL. D. head pores, NMMB-P7012, arrow indicates the ST pore." ;
